    <p><strong>We don't do:</strong> residential induction cooktops on this page (separate equipment category and consumer service track); induction cookware sales (chefs need ferrous cookware, but we don't sell it, we educate and refer); building circuit work (240V or higher amp circuits to the cooktop are electrical contractor scope); new induction installation (specialty installer trade); custom cooking suite fabrication or modification (metal fabricator trade).</p>
